subject: Nixon Watches and Premium Accessories
description: Nixon is an American watches, accessories and audio brand founded in 1997 in Encinitas, California.[1] Focused on the youth lifestyle market, Nixon’s range of team-designed, custom-built products was first introduced at retail via independent boardsport retailers, including surf, skate, & snow shops.
